<lb n="0780b02"/><head type="no">No. 687</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0780b03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0780008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0780008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】<app><lem resp="CBETA.march">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app>【元】<app><lem resp="CBETA.march">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app>【明】<app><lem resp="CBETA.march">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0780008"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>孝子經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0780b04"/>
<lb n="0780b05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0780009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（失譯…晉錄））＝失譯【宋】【元】，失譯人名【明】</note><note n="0780009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（失譯…晉錄））＝失譯【宋】【元】，＝失譯人名【明】</note><app n="0780009" word-count="9"><lem>失譯<note n="0780010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人名〕－【宮】</note><app n="0780010"><lem>人名</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>今附西晉錄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">失譯</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">失譯人名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0780b06"/><p>佛問諸沙門。親之生子。懷<note n="0780011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝抱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝抱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780011"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">抱</rdg></app>十月。身為重
<lb n="0780b07"/>病。臨生之日母危父怖。其情難言。既生之
<lb n="0780b08"/>後推燥臥濕。精誠之至血化為乳。摩<note n="0780012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拭＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拭＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780012"><lem>拭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飾</rdg></app>澡
<lb n="0780b09"/>浴。衣食教詔。禮賂師友。<note n="0780013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奉＝重【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉＝重【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780013"><lem>奉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">重</rdg></app>貢君長。子顏和
<lb n="0780b10"/>悅親亦欣豫。子設慘<note n="0780014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慼＝戚【三】</note><note n="0780014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慼＝戚【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0780014"><lem>慼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">戚</rdg></app>親心焦枯。<note n="0780015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（出門…之））八字＝入門存之出顧履履【宮】</note><app n="0780015" word-count="8"><lem>出門愛
<lb n="0780b11"/>念入則存之</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">入門存之出顧履履</rdg></app>。心懷惕惕懼其不<note n="0780016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＝成【宮】</note><app n="0780016"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>。親恩若
<lb n="0780b12"/><note n="0780017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＋（當）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＋（當）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780017"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">此當</rdg></app>何以報<note n="0780018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780018"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。諸沙門對曰。唯當盡禮慈心
<lb n="0780b13"/>供養以賽<note n="0780019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＝養【宮】</note><app n="0780019"><lem>親</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">養</rdg></app><note n="0780020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恩＋（耳）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恩＋（耳）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780020"><lem>恩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">恩耳</rdg></app>。世尊又曰。子之養親。甘露
<lb n="0780b14"/>百味以<note n="0780021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恣＝咨【宮】</note><app n="0780021"><lem>恣</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">咨</rdg></app>其口。天樂眾音以娛其耳。名衣
<lb n="0780b15"/>上服光耀其<note n="0780022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＝體【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身＝體【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780022"><lem>身</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">體</rdg></app>。兩肩荷負周流四海。訖子
<lb n="0780b16"/>年命以賽<note n="0780023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">養恩＝恩養【三】</note><note n="0780023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">養恩＝恩養【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0780023"><lem>養恩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">恩養</rdg></app>。可謂孝乎。諸沙門曰。<note n="0780024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【宮】</note><app n="0780024"><lem>惟</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>
<lb n="0780b17"/>孝之大莫尚<note n="0780025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝干【宮】</note><app n="0780025"><lem>乎</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">干</rdg></app>茲。世尊<note n="0780026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔告〕－【宮】</note><app n="0780026"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>曰。未為孝矣。若
<lb n="0780b18"/>親頑闇不奉三尊。兇虐殘戾。濫竊非<note n="0780027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">理婬&CB00105;＝物情染【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">理婬&CB00105;＝物情染【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780027"><lem>理。婬
<lb n="0780b19"/>&CB00105;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">物情染</rdg></app>外色。偽辭非道。<note n="0780028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酖愐＝耽醉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酖愐＝耽醉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780028"><lem>酖愐</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">耽醉</rdg></app>荒亂。違背正真兇
<lb n="0780b20"/>&CB00859;若<note n="0780029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斯＝此【宮】</note><app n="0780029"><lem>斯</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>。子當極諫以啟悟之。<note n="0780030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【宮】</note><app n="0780030"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>猶瞢瞢未
<lb n="0780b21"/>悟。即為<note n="0780031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">義化當＝開化【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義化當＝開化【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780031"><lem>義化當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">開化</rdg></app>。牽<note n="0780032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">譬＝&CB13520;【宮】</note><app n="0780032"><lem>譬</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB13520;</rdg></app>引類示王者之牢獄。
<lb n="0780b22"/>諸囚之刑戮曰。斯為不軌。身被眾毒。自招
<lb n="0780b23"/>殞命。命終神去繫于太山。湯火萬毒獨<note n="0780033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呼＝喚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呼＝喚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780033"><lem>呼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">喚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0780b24"/>無救。由彼履惡遭<note n="0780034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斯＝此【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0780034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斯＝此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0780034"><lem>斯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>重殃<note n="0780035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矣設＝若【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矣設＝若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780035"><lem>矣。設</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>復未移。
<lb n="0780b25"/><note n="0780036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吟＝悲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吟＝悲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780036"><lem>吟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悲</rdg></app>泣啼<note n="0780037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嗷＝號【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嗷＝號【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780037"><lem>嗷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">號</rdg></app>絕<note n="0780038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝無【宮】</note><app n="0780038"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>飲食。親雖不明。必以恩
<lb n="0780b26"/>愛之痛懼子死矣。<note n="0780039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝由【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">猶＝由【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780039"><lem>猶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">由</rdg></app>當強忍伏心崇<note n="0780040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（正）＋道【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（正）＋道【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780040"><lem>道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">正道</rdg></app>。若
<lb n="0780b27"/>親遷志奉佛五戒。仁<note n="0780041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惻＝測【明】，懼【宮】</note><note n="0780041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惻＝測【明】，＝懼【宮】</note><app n="0780041"><lem>惻</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">測</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">懼</rdg></app>不殺。清讓不盜。貞
<lb n="0780b28"/>潔不婬。守信不欺。孝順不醉<note n="0780042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780042"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。宗門之內。
<lb n="0780b29"/>即<note n="0780043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＋（父）【宮】</note><app n="0780043"><lem>親</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">親父</rdg></app>慈子孝。夫正婦貞。九族和睦僕使<note n="0780044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">順從＝恭順【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">順從＝恭順【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780044"><lem>順
<pb ed="T" id="T16.0687.0780c" n="0780c"/>
<lb n="0780c01"/>從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">恭順</rdg></app>。潤澤遠被含血受恩。十方諸佛天龍鬼神。
<lb n="0780c02"/>有道之君。忠平之臣。黎庶萬姓無不敬愛。祐
<lb n="0780c03"/>而安之。<note n="0780045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">數＝雖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">數＝雖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780045"><lem>數</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雖</rdg></app>有顛倒之政。&CB02439;<note n="0780046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嬖＝&CB00858;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嬖＝&CB00858;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780046"><lem>嬖</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00858;</rdg></app>之輔。兇兒妖
<lb n="0780c04"/>婦。千邪萬怪。無如已何。<note n="0780047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝如【宮】</note><app n="0780047"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>是二親處世常
<lb n="0780c05"/>安。壽終魂靈<note n="0780048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">往＝昇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">往＝昇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780048"><lem>往</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">昇</rdg></app>生天上。諸佛共會得聞法
<lb n="0780c06"/>言。獲道度世長與苦別</p>
<lb n="0780c07"/><p>佛告諸沙門。&CB00418;世無孝唯斯為孝耳能令<note n="0780049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（二）＋親【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（二）＋親【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780049"><lem>親</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">二親</rdg></app>
<lb n="0780c08"/>去惡為善。奉持五戒。執三<note n="0780050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝貞【宮】</note><app n="0780050"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">貞</rdg></app>歸。朝奉而暮
<lb n="0780c09"/>終者。恩重於親乳哺之養無量之惠。若不能
<lb n="0780c10"/>以三尊之至化其親者。雖為<note n="0780051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">孝＝前【宮】</note><app n="0780051"><lem>孝</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">前</rdg></app>養<note n="0780052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝由【宮】</note><app n="0780052"><lem>猶</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">由</rdg></app><note n="0780053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為不孝＝不孝矣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為不孝＝不孝矣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780053"><lem>為不
<lb n="0780c11"/>孝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不孝矣</rdg></app>。無以&CB00858;妻遠賢不親。女情多欲好色無倦。
<lb n="0780c12"/>違孝<note n="0780054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殺＝敬【宮】</note><app n="0780054"><lem>殺</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">敬</rdg></app>親。國政荒亂。萬民流<note n="0780055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亡＝忘【宮】</note><app n="0780055"><lem>亡</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">忘</rdg></app>。本志惠
<lb n="0780c13"/>施。<note n="0780056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮＝以【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮＝以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780056"><lem>禮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app><note n="0780057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">式＝戒【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780057"><lem>式</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">戒</rdg></app>自<note n="0780058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">撿＝檢【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780058"><lem>撿</lem><rdg wit="【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">檢</rdg></app>。<note n="0780059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔軟〕－【宮】</note><app n="0780059"><lem>軟</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>心祟仁。<note n="0780060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">烝烝＝蒸蒸【三】，拯【宮】</note><note n="0780060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">烝烝＝蒸蒸【宋】【元】【明】，＝拯【宮】</note><app n="0780060"><lem>烝烝</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">蒸蒸</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">拯</rdg></app>進德。潛
<lb n="0780c14"/>意寂寞。學志叡達。名<note n="0780061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">動＝勳【宮】</note><app n="0780061"><lem>動</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">勳</rdg></app>諸天。明齊賢者。自
<lb n="0780c15"/>穢妻聚。惑志女色。荒迷<note n="0780062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于＝子【宮】</note><app n="0780062"><lem>于</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">子</rdg></app>欲。妖<note n="0780063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱姿態＝治恣能【宮】</note><app n="0780063"><lem>蠱姿態</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">治恣能</rdg></app>其
<lb n="0780c16"/>變萬端。薄智之夫。淺見之士。&CB00418;其如此。不
<lb n="0780c17"/><note n="0780064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">覺＝學【宮】</note><app n="0780064"><lem>覺</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">學</rdg></app>微漸遂迴志沒身。從彼<note n="0780065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魃魅＝妖媚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">魃魅＝妖媚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780065"><lem>魃魅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">妖媚</rdg></app>邪巧之<note n="0780066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亂＝辭【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亂＝辭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780066"><lem>亂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">辭</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0780c18"/>或危親殺君。<note n="0780067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00385;＝悟【宮】</note><app n="0780067"><lem>&CB00385;</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">悟</rdg></app>色情蕩。忿<note n="0780068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嫉＝戾【宮】</note><app n="0780068"><lem>嫉</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">戾</rdg></app>怠慢。散心盲
<lb n="0780c19"/><note n="0780069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冥＝瞑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">冥＝瞑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780069"><lem>冥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">瞑</rdg></app>。等行鳥獸。自古世來無不由之<note n="0780070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殺＝亡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780070" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殺＝亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780070"><lem>殺</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亡</rdg></app>身滅
<pb ed="T" id="T16.0687.0781a" n="0781a"/>
<lb n="0781a01"/>宗。是以沙門獨而不雙。清潔其志<note n="0781001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝唯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781001"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>道是
<lb n="0781a02"/>務。奉<app type="＊" source="0780034"><lem>斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此</rdg></app>明<note n="0781002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戒＝教【宮】</note><app n="0781002"><lem>戒</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">教</rdg></app>。為君即保四海。為臣即忠。
<lb n="0781a03"/>以仁養民。<note n="0781003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔即〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781003"><lem>即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>父法明子孝慈。夫信婦貞。優
<lb n="0781a04"/>婆塞優婆夷執行如<note n="0781004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝此【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781004"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>。世世逢佛見法得道。
<lb n="0781a05"/>佛說如是。弟子歡喜</p>
<lb n="0781a06"/><trailer><title><app type="＊" source="0780008"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>孝子<note n="0781005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宋】【元】</note><app n="0781005"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">經一卷</rdg></app></title></trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
